e":75,"text":240,"spans":241,"direction":78},"Et si votre plus belle victoire était celle que vous remportiez sur vous-même ? Rejoignez-nous sur le tatami pour transformer votre énergie et cultiver la sérénité.",[],{"link_type":55,"key":243,"url":89,"text":244},"23203e95-3868-4e04-b856-c2e2f1817d60","VENEZ ESSAYER : VOTRE PREMIER COURS EST OFFERT !","showcase$c21c1cae-fc21-41dc-b51e-47ec482364d0","showcase",{"variation":69,"version":70,"items":248,"primary":249,"id":343,"slice_type":45,"slice_label":5},[],{"title":250,"body":254,"focuses":258},[251],{"type":105,"text":252,"spans":253,"direction":78},"La Maîtrise des 3 Armes",[],[255],{"type":75,"text":256,"spans":257,"direction":78},"Découvrez notre pratique de l'Aïkido",[],[259,284,302,319],{"link":260},{"id":261,"type":45,"tags":262,"lang":14,"slug":263,"first_publication_date":264,"last_publication_date":265,"uid":263,"url":266,"data":267,"link_type":38,"key":283,"isBroken":40},"agLgwRAAACcATZZo",[],"la-maitrise-des-3-armes","2026-05-12T08:41:52+0000","2026-05-12T20:23:19+0000","\u002Ffocus\u002Fla-maitrise-des-3-armes",{"title":268,"description":272,"cover":276},[269],{"type":270,"text":252,"spans":271,"direction":78},"heading1",[],[273],{"type":75,"text":274,"spans":275,"direction":78},"Contrairement à une pratique purement sportive, nous enseignons l'Aïkido dans sa globalité. Vous apprendrez le maniement du Bokken (sabre en bois), du Jo (bâton) et du Tanto (couteau), piliers indispensables pour comprendre les déplacements et la précision des techniques à mains nues.",[],{"dimensions":277,"alt":5,"copyright":5,"url":280,"id":281,"edit":282},{"width":278,"height":279},2816,1536,"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.prismic.io\u002Faikido-traditionnel-cotiere\u002FagLnvKYofJOwHHC5_Gemini_Generated_Image_qp7a9eqp7a9eqp7a.png?auto=format,compress","agLnvKYofJOwHHC5",{"x":26,"y":26,"zoom":27,"background":28},"cb5ce3cf-536d-49fa-9c9a-bf4313dd1bf3",{"link":285},{"id":44,"type":45,"tags":286,"lang":14,"slug":47,"first_publication_